  "2026-07-19T12:50:17.697Z",maintainer-agent,"Release-gate evidence: pnpm release:gates completed build, typecheck, docs/skills, static quality, package boundary, token budget, 5,963 tests with exact 100/100/100/100 coverage, version/sync, secret scan, packed-package smoke, and package-first dogfood successfully. The aggregate command stopped only at its intentional Greptile stage because Greptile requires a committed diff against main; the local commit will be reviewed before push."
  "2026-07-19T13:48:05.381Z",maintainer-agent,"PR #616 round-one review follow-up: unmatched_ids now compares requested IDs against a separate unfiltered, unpaged all-status existence query, so limit/offset and additional filters cannot misclassify existing items. Added paged and filtered-existing regression cases."
